ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I might recommend it for basic students. I don't think it is appropriate for more advanced students. It is too basic.
It is an overview of evolution, focusing on the basic theories and definitions. I would recommend it to students who do not have much of a background in ecology or evolution.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The project was useful at the end
The course deepened my knowledge olf the specifics of evolution, which is a topic I hope to pursue in some form in one of my discourses.
